    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>*<persName key="#Bishops #Popes #Papal_concession #Witness" ref="#people/51"
                            >Innocentius</persName>* <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Popes">servus servorum</rs> Dei. Dilectis filiis <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/3568">Henrico</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Abbots #Imperial/royal_diploma #Papal_concession #Curtes #Forests #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Houses"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti supra Padum</orgName>
                        eiusque fratribus tam presentibus quam futuris imperpetuum. Apostolice Sedis
                        officio ac debito commonemus honestas et religiosas personas diligere et
                        earum quieti atque utilitati auxiliante domino salubriter providere.
                        Eapropter dillecti in Domino filii vestris desideriis accomodantes assensum,
                            <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">concessionem</rs> ab illustri filio
                        nostro <persName key="#Emperor/king #Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            ref="#people/3578">Lothario</persName>, glorioso Romanorum <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">Imperatore</rs> Augusto, in <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Forests #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Houses"
                            ref="#estates/42"><rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                            <placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Forests #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Houses"
                                ref="#places/34">Pigugnaie</placeName></geogName> devocionis intuitu
                        vobis factam, auctoritate nostra firmamus. Statuentes ut ea que in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cereals">aratoriis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, aut <rs
                            key="#Houses">domibus</rs>, aut aliis quibuscumque prefatus augustus in
                        eodem loco vobis concessisse cognoscitur, firma vobis imperpetuum et
                        illibata serventur. Salva nimirum <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1100"
                            >Sancte Romane Ecclesie</orgName> matris vestre iusticia. Nulli ergo
                        hominum fas sit super eadem nostra <rs key="#Papal_concession"
                            >confirmacione</rs> vos [t]emere turbare aut aliquam vobis exinde
                        inminucionem vel contrarietatem inferre. Si quis autem ausu temerario hoc
                        attemptare presumpserit, indignacionem omnipotentis Dei, et beatorum Petri
                        et Pauli apostolorurn eius incurrat. + Ego INNOCEncius catholice Ecclesie
                        episcopus <rs key="#Witness">SS.</rs> Data <placeName ref="#places/66"
                            >Pisis</placeName> per manum <persName
                            key="#Deacons #Cardinals #Chancellor #Papal_concession"
                            ref="#people/3563">AIMERICIS</persName> Sancte Romane Ecclesie <rs
                            key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cardinals">cardinalis</rs> et <rs key="#Chancellor"
                            >cancellarius</rs>, II Kalendas Marcii, indictione XIII, incarnacionis
                        dominice ANNO Millesimo C.XXXVI. Pontificatus dompni INNocencij pape II,
                        anno SEPTIMO. </ab>
                </div>
